<br>
so here goes: <br>
<br>
I believe that all art is valid. but what is art? well, everything is art, if it has been drawn/painted/sculped/created/designed with feeling, and with the deliberate intention of causing an emotional response. wether the response is 'good' or 'bad' matters little, as long as the response is there. any topic is as valid as any other, and likewise, any medium is just as valid as any other. all works of art are equally important, nomatter who creates them, and nomatter what motivation the artist actually has to create them. all art is valid.<br>
<br>
 <p>remember: it's nice to be important - but it's more important to be nice<br>
<br>
