<br>
You can compare Michelangelo to a child in that each may have put the same percent of work into their potential at the time.  Just because the majority favors Michelangelo's medium, does not exactly prove that it is more meaningful than a stick figure of a child's imagination.<br>
<br>
But it's all subjective right? <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.geocities.com/six6jin/ezaccount/bubble.txt"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
